<div class="msgContentFrame">Kao, I have a suggestion:  Couldn't you guys ask each board to compile all its best threads, including any current stickies, into one master sticky?  Then you'd only have to deal with one or two stickies per forum, and new sticky-worthy posts could just be added to the master list by the board members?  It'd clear up some of the boards and free you guys up from having to deal with sticky requests.  Plus, I think it'd be helpful to the site visitors to have all the best info from each board available in one big post for ease in finding it.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>WoW: <br />Saboruto - Night Elf Druid <br />Zami - Troll Shaman <br />Shadow Council Realm</div><!--[if IE 7]><hr class="msgIE7fill"/><![endif]--></div>
